headline: Argus cuts Domino’s rating to hold on cost pressures, weak U.S. sales
summary: Investing.com -- Argus downgraded Domino’s Pizza Inc (NYSE:DPZ) to Hold from Buy, citing higher food and labour costs as well as weak consumer spending at U.S. restaurants.
